Package com.natwest.opendata.configuration

Class SDKCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.natwest.opendata.configuration.SDKCache
  • public class SDKCache
extends java.lang.Object

    SDKCache is used to store recently used data in HashMap with RLU technique using doubly Linked List. It contains the value in the form of key and value pair. It reduces the number of API hits as much as possible and has the configurable capacity for storing the data. If data exceed from capacity it will remove least recently used Data from cache and add recently used data. If capacity is not exceed, it will add recently used data.
